      "fontSize": 20.851840549045136,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Notes:\n• Subagents share KnowledgeBaseTool and UpdateChatStateTool\n• Cards (Learn, Prepare, Reflect) are JSON in the agent text response — not a tool\n• Orchestrator classifies intent and hands off; subagents stream user-facing dialogue\n• Tool request/response pairs stay in the conversation chain as ordinary messages",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Notes:\n• Subagents share KnowledgeBaseTool and UpdateChatStateTool\n• Cards (Learn, Prepare, Reflect) are JSON in the agent text response — not a tool\n• Orchestrator classifies intent and hands off; subagents stream user-facing dialogue\n• Tool request/response pairs stay in the conversation chain as ordinary messages",
      "index": "aH",
      "frameId": null,
      "autoResize": true,
