    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 2355,
      "versionNonce": 1148376204,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "id": "AE3E5VGoEuWvmZGLzc_SS",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "x": 986.7193170041874,
      "y": -211.10430702994938,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "width": 919.6791381835938,
      "height": 520,
      "seed": 1559389932,
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781959186357,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "1. Ingress — POST/streaming; JWT auth; rate limits\n2. Guardrail check — input guardrail before any LLM call\n3. Persistence — user message → PostgreSQL; question copied to background \nthread for memory extraction\n4. Memory retrieve — relevant facts from memory layer (vector search)\n5. Agent selection — chat state: Orchestrator, Learn, Prepare, or Reflect\n6. Prompt assembly — system prompt, history (incl. tool pairs), new question, \ntool defs, memory facts last\n7. LLM call with tools — KnowledgeBaseTool + UpdateChatStateTool\n8. Tool loop — KB retrieval, UpdateChatStateTool if needed; stream final answer via SSE\n9. Output guardrails — checked every N chars during stream\n10. Completion — response persisted; background tasks: memory write, search index, telemetry\n11. Artifact generation — subagent emits {...} JSON; frontend parses and POSTs as JSONB",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Ingress — POST/streaming; JWT auth; rate limits\n2. Guardrail check — input guardrail before any LLM call\n3. Persistence — user message → PostgreSQL; question copied to background \nthread for memory extraction\n4. Memory retrieve — relevant facts from memory layer (vector search)\n5. Agent selection — chat state: Orchestrator, Learn, Prepare, or Reflect\n6. Prompt assembly — system prompt, history (incl. tool pairs), new question, \ntool defs, memory facts last\n7. LLM call with tools — KnowledgeBaseTool + UpdateChatStateTool\n8. Tool loop — KB retrieval, UpdateChatStateTool if needed; stream final answer via SSE\n9. Output guardrails — checked every N chars during stream\n10. Completion — response persisted; background tasks: memory write, search index, telemetry\n11. Artifact generation — subagent emits {...} JSON; frontend parses and POSTs as JSONB",
      "index": "aw",
      "frameId": null,
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 2
    },
